;\">戴上了有色眼鏡</span><br />\n罔顧自由市場規則<br />\n摧毀香港營商環境<br />\n黑暴之下豈有完卵<br />\n順我者昌逆我者亡<br />\n封閉和自毁的斷崖<br />\n渺小又卑鄙的幻想<br />\n黑社會的敲詐勒索<br />\n洗腦式的教條主義<br />\n比邪教組織更兇狠<br />\n義和團幫襯義和團<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港應該是彩色的</span><br />\n污染社會的現代氣象<br />\n摧毀香港經濟汽油彈<br />\n極端的政治廣告平台<br />\n點解消費仲要分顏色<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">只是反對派的信號彈</span><br />\n對藍店威力只是皮外傷<br />\n也許死得比任何人更難看"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:06:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e127fd3a9d984680121c3a54c7b9f1defd81bd2","tid":2002042,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:06:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2530000/2532737/reuters_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2530000%2F2532737%2Freuters_1024.jpg&h=1565933d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.silentmajority.hk/img/2019/12/20191231_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.silentmajority.hk%2Fimg%2F2019%2F12%2F20191231_2.jpg&h=69f73012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/yellow-04_uRYUe_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fyellow-04_uRYUe_1200x0.png&h=95072a35&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"853d54c1cf3e8704e18569ff4f7cce4f3102499a","tid":2002042,"uid":3962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:06:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9uxRgYz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9uxRgYz.gif&h=4cf9b760&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13394d17f6ecb3171fd7663e4535fb57f0765c95","tid":2002042,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:07:16.000Z","msg":"唔畀黃色經濟圈發展就真係抹殺原本多彩嘅香港啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hk